FBIS3-17636 "drsov059_t_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-059 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Mar 1994 BALTIC STATES Estonia Ostankino TV Cut Due to Contract Expiry, Debts LD2803091094 Tallinn Radio Tallinn Network in Estonian 0600 GMT 28 Mar 94 LD2803091094 Tallinn Radio Tallinn Network Language: Estonian Article Type:BFN [Text] According to a goverment resolution, Estonian Telecom will today end relays of the Russian Ostankino State Radio and Television Company programs. The government resolution is due to both the contract expiry date and Ostankino's debt to Telecom. Government press representative Ain Saarna has said that Ostankino's debt to Estonian Telecom amounts to 185,000 German marks. Making allowances to viewers' requests, Telecom will continue to relay the Mexican television serial Simply Maria.
